data.description: Beautiful home in a great location! Gorgeous 5 bed 3 bath home on a corner lot in the Wind Rose Subdivision Edinburg off of Canton, between Sugar and Jackson.  This home features granite throughout, tile and hardwood floors, updated fixtures, extensive storage, nice yard, and lots of extras. Love entertaining? This is it! Perfect patio space for family and friends with plenty of room for seating, bricks stone oven, bar area, and space for an outdoor kitchen. Up to 10k in seller concessions for qualified buyers!  Schedule you showing now!
